The '''Month of Plenty''' was a [[Weequay/Legends|Weequay]] [[Holiday|holy season]] that honored the [[Moon/Legends|moon]] god [[Quay]]. Temples on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Sriluur/Legends|Sriluur]] which were dedicated to Quay had an open skylight in their roof which allowed Weequay priests to track the moon's progress during the month.

